{"tid":13979,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"人類自由指數排行 台灣第26 香港全球第一","createTime":"2016-11-30T10:10:46.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-30T11:13:51.000Z","uid":1971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c05baed472e9bcc91ef202eebcdbdb52cd83e816","tid":13979,"uid":1971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T10:10:46.000Z","msg":"〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕加拿大研究機構「The Fraser Institute」公布最新一份「人類<br />\n自由指數」報告，台灣在全球159個國家中排名第26，滿分10分的標準中得到8.18分。<br />\n<br />\n該份報告將評分項目分為「個人自由」與「經濟自由」兩大類，並在兩大指標中細分數十<br />\n個項目進行評分。台灣在個人自由分數為8.71，排行31位；經濟自由分數為7.65，排行第<br />\n23位。雖然台灣排名位居前段班，但與過去幾年相比略有退步，也是自2010年以來排行最<br />\n低的一年。<br />\n<br />\n其它值得關注的部分，排行前十名的地區分別為：1.香港、2.瑞士、3.紐西蘭、4.愛爾蘭<br />\n、5.丹麥、6.加拿大、7.澳洲、8.英國、9.芬蘭、10.荷蘭，中國則排在141名幾乎墊底。<br />\n有研究員指出，自由指數並非用來衡量民主程度，但中國若破壞一國兩制，香港的排名可<br />\n能會下降。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/1902319\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F1902319&d=7O3ztiABqAoAY%2BrF22wgzYscwJTI%2BQouKF8MUrnyvY0%3D&h=b7c282c9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F1902319&h=278c86f3\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/1902319</a><br />\n<br />\n唔講咁多 英英好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9096f8f46c403002bb07a749059a6b0e5010001f","tid":13979,"uid":1971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T10:25:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8f4f203c2f5cbaa36f35a8b2da803017c956f10","tid":13979,"uid":3987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T10:26:50.000Z","msg":"美國呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd42dc35f2748c4e16621d147c37e34435fdbd81","tid":13979,"uid":42246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T10:27:57.000Z","msg":"On9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  土生土長既香港人<br />\n絕望多過希望 邊撚到來自由<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9cd62c4ea08810c2f5b0f71d2b30c8c8e4bb6f6","tid":13979,"uid":1971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T10:36:58.000Z","msg":"呢啲排名其實係咪比錢買？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n記得之前有個係香港環境最好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5a0b464d4f606350bcdaadd9163ba4c9eda1562","tid":13979,"uid":1971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T11:13:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}